#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nancumsum.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nancumsum"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the cumulative sum of tensor elements over a given axis treating "
"Not a Numbers (NaNs) as zero.  The cumulative sum does not change when "
"NaNs are encountered and leading NaNs are replaced by zeros."
msgstr ""
"返回在给定轴上将 NaN（非数字）视为零的张量元素的累积和。当遇到 NaN 时，"
"累积和不会改变，且开头的 NaN 会被替换为零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:5 of
msgid "Zeros are returned for slices that are all-NaN or empty."
msgstr "对于全部为 NaN 或空的切片，将返回零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:7 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:9 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the cumulative sum is computed. The default (None) is to"
" compute the cumsum over the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算累积和的轴。默认值（None）是对展平的张量进行 cumsum 计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:12 of
msgid ""
"Type of the returned tensor and of the accumulator in which the elements "
"are summed.  If `dtype` is not specified, it defaults to the dtype of "
"`a`, unless `a` has an integer dtype with a precision less than that of "
"the default platform integer.  In that case, the default platform integer"
" is used."
msgstr ""
"返回张量的类型和元素求和的累加器的类型。如果未指定 `dtype`，则默认为 `a` "
"的 dtype，除非 `a` 是精度低于默认平台整数的整数类型。在这种情况下，将使用"
"默认平台整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:18 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape and buffer length as the expected output but the type will be "
"cast if necessary. See `doc.ufuncs` (Section \"Output arguments\") for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。它必须具有与预期输出相同的形状和缓冲区长度，"
"但类型在必要时会进行转换。有关更多详细信息，请参见 `doc.ufuncs`（“输出"
"参数”一节）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:24 of
msgid ""
"**nancumsum** -- A new tensor holding the result is returned unless `out`"
" is specified, in which it is returned. The result has the same size as "
"`a`, and the same shape as `a` if `axis` is not None or `a` is a 1-d "
"tensor."
msgstr ""
"**nancumsum** —— 除非指定了 `out`，否则将返回一个包含结果的新张量。结果的"
"大小与 `a` 相同，如果 `axis` 不为 None 或者 `a` 是一维张量，则形状也相同"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.cumsum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:33 of
msgid "Cumulative sum across tensor propagating NaNs."
msgstr "沿张量传播 NaN 的累积和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumsum.nancumsum:36 of
msgid "Show which elements are NaN."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是 NaN。"

